                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Wilson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santiago</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-11-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">November 10, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Wilson reports that the claims convention with the Government of the United
                    States has been approved by the Congress of Chile, with two amendments by the
                    House.)</p>
            </div>
